summary: i love how so many people draw joxter with a fashion sense when i, as someone who has never read/watched any of the moomins and...
body: i love how so many people draw joxter with a fashion sense when i, as someone who has never read/watched any of the moomins and learned everything i know about it from tumblr, would expect to hear rummaging outside in the middle of the night only to walk outside with a flashlight and find joxter digging through my garbage and holding the little flag from my mailbox because he stole it
